						<summary>Registers the gift of the whole village of Nallūr consisting of 360 <foreign>vēli</foreign> of land and of other pieces elsewhere amounting to ten <foreign>vēli</foreign> and odd with their income in taxes like <foreign>mākkalam</foreign>, <foreign>āyam</foreign> and <foreign>kīḻiṟaipāṭṭam</foreign> for the requirements of the temple of Nallanāyaṉār at Nallūr by Āḷappiṟandāṉ Mōgaṉ alias Kāḍavarāyaṉ.</summary>
					</msContents>
